1264945 36 Powers authority and responsibilities of municipalities.-
702655 1 The State Government as and when it considers expedient may, by notification, entrust-
1107195 athe municipalities with the function of-
221995 ithe preparation of plans for economic development and social justice;
1938341 iithe performance of functions and the implementation of schemes as may be entrusted to including those in relation to the matters listed in the Schedule;
