690792 iall interest and profit, arising from any investment of, or from any transaction in connection with, any money belonging to the Nagar Panchayat or the Council.
1479630 2Nothing in this section or in this Act shall affect any obligation of a Nagar Panchayat or or a Council arising from a trust legally imposed upon or accepted by the Nagar Panchayat or by the Council, as the case may be
