160849 abe served personally on or presented to the person to whom the same is addressed; or
1559720 bif it cannot be so served, presented or delivered, be affixed on some conspicuous part of his place of abode or of the land, building or other thing in respect of which the notice, bill, form, summons or notice of demand is intended to be served; or
1049805 cbe sent by post in registered cover.
