114688 iiform and manner in which the accounts of receipts and expenditures of a Nagar Panchayat or a Council shall be kept;
1025603 iiiform and manner in which the annual budget of a Nagar Panchayat or a Council shall be prepared;
1904984 ivmanner in which returns, statements and reports by a Nagar Panchayat or a Council shall be submitted;
123910 vmatter not specifically provided for in this Act for the valuation of holdings, for the assessment, collection and refund of taxes imposed under this Act;
534723 videtermination of fees payable upon distraint warrant under this Act;
1825047 viiregulation, management and inspection of the working systems of water- supply, lighting, drainage or sewerage provided, established or maintained by or under the control and administration of a Nagar Panchayat or a Council;
449559 viiiform and procedure for taking oath or affirmation by Chairperson, Vice- Chairperson and Councillors, he authority who shall administer oath or affirmation; and
536280 ixmanner in which bye- laws shall be published after confirmation by the Government.
911543 3Every rule made under this Act shall be laid, as soon as may be after it is made, before Legislative Assembly while it is in session for a total period of thirty days which may be comprised in one session or in two or more successive sessions, and if, before the expiry of the session in which it is so laid or the session immediately following the session or the successive sessions aforesaid, Legislative Assembly makes any modification in the rule or decides that any such rule should not be made, the rule shall thereafter have effect only in such modified form or be of no effect, as the case may be; so, however, that any such modification or annulment shall be without prejudice to the validity of anything previously done under that rule.
